race.comment: CRAIG KEEPING (3) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at this track over 425m behind Birdwood Franky (24.71) in a Grade 5. Can atone. NED THE KNIGHT (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from nine tries. Was out of the placings last time (24.67) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 3.5 lengths. Can feature in the finish. HELLO COOPER (8) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at this track over 425m behind Daintree Pedro (24.73) in a Grade 5. Warrants plenty of respect. PERFECT REVENGE (1) can sneak into the finish with the right run.
